-- Galp Says Brazilian Deepwater Well Confirms Potential of Light Oil in Tupi
-- B y   B r i a n   S w i n t
-- 2010-10-07T06:20:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-07/galp-says-brazilian-deepwater-well-confirms-potential-of-light-oil-in-tupi.html
Galp Energia SGPS SA said that a new
well in the deepwater Santos Basin off the coast of Brazil
confirmed potential resources of 5 billion to 8 billion barrels
of oil and natural gas at the Tupi field.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Brian Swint at 
 bswint@bloomberg.net  